// R37/AN13/L3-PY (2026-04-18): original script delegated all R2 operations
// (list/prune/upload) to `scripts/r2_upload.py` via shell-wrapped python3.
// Wrapper-fallback python3 calls removed. See CLAUDE.md §.py 절대 금지.
